{"id":681787,"title":"04｜目标的本质与三种类型","content":"","comments":[{"had_liked":false,"id":379426,"user_name":"进化菌","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1276861,"ip_address":"广东","ucode":"B30A5F78BB4171","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/7b/bd/ccb37425.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1691936382,"is_pvip":true,"replies":null,"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":4,"score":2,"product_id":100610401,"comment_content":"目的的本质是什么？目标是一种个人或是系统想要达到的结果，而且会为此计划，设法达成。可实现的是目标，不可实现的是欲望、白日梦。\n\n目标有三种类型：期待超过现状（如何提升），期待维持现状（如何避免伤害），期待回到过往（如何恢复原状）。\n我们更关注期待超过现状，常常忘记后面的两种，以为那不是目标。","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1421980,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/15/b2/9c/b7b9896c.jpg","nickname":"王云峰","note":"","ucode":"699E46BE31495B","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":638838,"discussion_content":"我觉得只有第一种是目标，后两种太懈怠了，不进则退哪有保持","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1709984979,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"浙江","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]}]}